items.headline: Drive into the Colin McRae Rally WIkia
items.desc: The Colin McRae Ralley Wikia community was created by fans of the Colin McRae Rally series of games which includes ten games in the Rally and DiRT series. The first game was released in 1998 and the latest, DiRT Showdown, was released May 2012. This wiki attempts to chronicle all the information regarding these games - including tracks, cars, characters, drivers, and more.
